{"tid":1582619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"欲與怪物戰鬥，就不要成為廢物","createTime":"2019-09-20T07:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T10:27:31.000Z","uid":50904,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"636669818f2effe9d10a23630f8dc42fa090df52","tid":1582619,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">反抗暴政，需要勇氣;思考策略需要理性;和平手段或武力抗爭皆為手段而已</span></strong><br />\n認為只一種方法可以成功，就係教條主義<br />\n<br />\nYou can't truly call yourself &quot;peaceful&quot; unless you are capable of great violence.<br />\nIf you're not capable of violence, you're not peaceful, you're harmless.<br />\nImportant distinction.<br />\n一句意譯:<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「欲與怪物戰鬥，就不要成為廢物」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Sivis pacem, para bellum&quot; <br />\n&quot;if you want peace, prepare for war&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「汝欲和平，必先備戰」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n &quot;I must study politics and war, that our sons may have liberty to study mathematics and philosophy.&quot; - John Adams<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「我必須研習政治與戰爭，我們的下一代方能有修習數學和哲學的自由。」  - 約翰亞當斯</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n選舉近了，散水黨、留力黨、(海外)民意黨群空而出<br />\n希望大家思想都要Full Gear，靜靜地坐低花50分鐘睇哂下面呢個節目，認真思考武力抗爭背後嘅正當性同道德基礎<br />\n拒絕人云亦云、以比較正負評數目代替獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>RTHK 五夜講場 - 哲學有偈傾：勇武和理傾</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw5npso82pKs&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8gvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=119fe5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs</a>"},{"pid":"172cd18c6e50cbefef9ee56becdaf8e4f1200cf6","tid":1582619,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"覺得連登比人滲透? 通街三毛? 全部都係打手網軍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得個推字同正評係無用架，想反擊就入下條